{"tid":1933330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西總統之子直指疫情肆虐是中国的錯   中国大使 : 你感染精神病毒","createTime":"2020-03-19T08:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T02:19:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d9112a3d60151b7fc27f794061a40f7106b00d","tid":1933330,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:31:37.000Z","msg":"巴西受到新冠肺炎（COVID-19）衝擊，總統波索納洛（Jair Bolsonaro）在處理疫情方面則引發民眾不滿，許多國人紛紛要求他下台。對此，波索納洛的兒子愛德華多（Eduardo）則在推特嗆聲這是中國的錯；此舉引發中國駐巴西大使楊萬明怒火。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》報導，巴西多名政界高層中鏢，波索納洛此前還被媒體誤傳確診，他的國家安全顧問、礦業與能源部長、參議院議長都感染新冠肺炎，造成民眾恐慌。許多國人18日晚間在家裡的窗邊敲打鍋碗瓢盆，要求波索納洛「滾出去」。<br />\n<br />\n本身也是參議員的愛德華多隨後在推特發聲，他把中國比作車諾比核事故中的蘇聯，聲稱中方掩蓋事實，這是中國的錯誤，「自由才是解答。」<br />\n<br />\n    Quem assistiu Chernobyl vai entender o q ocorreu.Substitua a usina nuclear pelo coronav&iacute;rus e a ditadura sovi&eacute;tica pela chinesa<br />\n<br />\n    +1 vez uma ditadura preferiu esconder algo grave a expor tendo desgaste,mas q salvaria in&uacute;meras vidas<br />\n<br />\n    A culpa &eacute; da China e liberdade seria a solu&ccedil;&atilde;o <a href=\"https://t.co/h3jyGlPymv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fh3jyGlPymv&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=a014d938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/h3jyGlPymv</a><br />\n    &mdash; Eduardo Bolsonaro(@BolsonaroSP) March 18, 2020<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國駐巴西大使館回嗆指出，愛德華多的話語非常不負責任，「從邁阿密回國後，很不幸你感染了精神的病毒，這會影響我們人民的情誼。」楊萬明也透過推特指責，愛德華多邪惡污辱了中國，這並不符合他作為公眾人物的素質。<br />\n<br />\n    @BolsonaroSP As suas palavras s&atilde;o um insulto mal&eacute;fico contra a China e o povo chin&ecirc;s. Tal atitude flagrante anti-China n&atilde;o condiz com o seu estatuto como deputado federal, nem a sua qualidade como uma figura p&uacute;blica especial. @ernestofaraujo @RodrigoMaia @camaradeputados @<br />\n    &mdash; Yang Wanming (@WanmingYang) March 19, 2020<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200319/1671401.htm</code></pre>"},{"pid":"bb90d5bc2f739f72e7ae427d59eb7c7e5a49c60b","tid":1933330,"uid":9542,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:33:15.000Z","msg":"支那人啲外交開始癲撚左，講野以為無後果"},{"pid":"6bdc4ec5ebefa45b6120ab4df4ddaed8c641e833","tid":1933330,"uid":79117,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"bb90d5bc2f739f72e7ae427d59eb7c7e5a49c60b","tid":1933330,"uid":9542,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:33:15.000Z","msg":"支那人啲外交開始癲撚左，講野以為無後果"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:33:49.000Z","msg":"因為真係無。"},{"pid":"9aee550c911e37c1bd35541656d7921e23d80dd0","tid":1933330,"uid":60545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"支那狗害完人仲可以扮救世主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06589b814ccc27269add9141331edefa96fef450","tid":1933330,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bdc4ec5ebefa45b6120ab4df4ddaed8c641e833","tid":1933330,"uid":79117,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"bb90d5bc2f739f72e7ae427d59eb7c7e5a49c60b","tid":1933330,"uid":9542,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:33:15.000Z","msg":"支那人啲外交開始癲撚左，講野以為無後果"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:33:49.000Z","msg":"因為真係無。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c173742702cddefee9fe3661a3b1c18cb3802479","tid":1933330,"uid":79562,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"6bdc4ec5ebefa45b6120ab4df4ddaed8c641e833","tid":1933330,"uid":79117,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"bb90d5bc2f739f72e7ae427d59eb7c7e5a49c60b","tid":1933330,"uid":9542,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:33:15.000Z","msg":"支那人啲外交開始癲撚左，講野以為無後果"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:33:49.000Z","msg":"因為真係無。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020